Java program to find area of circle using bufferedreader

[Java program to find area of circle using bufferedreader](https://www.flowerbrackets.com/java-program-to-find-area-of-circle-using-bufferedreader/)

Hereâ€™s the java program.

import java.io.BufferedReader;
import java.io.IOException;
import java.io.InputStreamReader;
public class UsingBufferedReader
{
   public static void main(String[] args) throws NumberFormatException, IOException
   {
      BufferedReader br = new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(System.in));
      System.out.print("Please enter radius of circle: ");
      double radius = Double.parseDouble(br.readLine());
      double area = Math.PI * radius * radius;
      System.out.println("Area of circle using bufferedreader: " + area);
   }
}
